OL,3,CThe island pensioners taking the gym
OL,4,Cto the beach
OL,6,FWhen I was asked to film a group of
OL,7,Fpensioners on a beach in Guernsey on a
OL,8,Fcold November I had no idea how much
OL,9,Ffun it would be.
OL,11,FThe Rockfit sessions were started 8
OL,12,Fyears ago by local fitness trainer,
OL,13,FAndy Perkins, who felt that there was
OL,14,Fnothing like it on the island - Keep
OL,15,FFit classes for older people that
OL,16,Factually involved quite a lot of
OL,17,Factivity.
