OL,3,CThe island pensioners taking the gym
OL,4,Cto the beach
OL,6,FAnd they work at it! There's a lot of
OL,7,Fpuffing and panting and a LOT of
OL,8,Flaughter - when they can catch their
OL,9,Fbreaths. And the challenges are all
OL,10,Fmuch more interesting than just
OL,11,Flifting weights in a gym.
OL,13,FKeep Fit enthusiast Megs Bailey says:
OL,14,F"I don't like exercise at all, but I
OL,15,Flove this group. It's outdoors, it's
OL,16,Fgiving me more balance - more focus on
OL,17,Fmy body - and I'm running now. I've
OL,18,Fnever run before in my life.
