OL,3,CThe island pensioners taking the gym
OL,4,Cto the beach
OL,6,F"I wouldn't normally go to a gym ever,
OL,7,Fbut being outside - watching the beach
OL,8,Fand watching the sea - it's wonderful
OL,9,Fand it's a lot of fun!"
OL,11,FAndy Perkins, who runs the group,
OL,12,Fsays: "There's plenty of exercise
OL,13,Foptions for people up to 50 that is
OL,14,Fmore high intensity in nature or at
OL,15,Fthe other end of the scale, things
OL,16,Fthat were more sedentary, but nothing
OL,17,Freally in the middle to help and
OL,18,Fencourage people that are over 60 to
OL,19,Fstay active."
