OL,3,CThe island pensioners taking the gym
OL,4,Cto the beach
OL,6,FThe sessions are run twice a week and
OL,7,Fusually on a beach, depending on the
OL,8,Fweather... and the tides.
OL,10,FMany friendships have been forged in
OL,11,Fthese sessions and everyone says
OL,12,Fthey're fitter than ever.
OL,14,FThe Keep Fit participants were
OL,15,Finterviewed as part of ITV Channel's
OL,16,F'My Community Series' which celebrates
OL,17,Fthe importance of coming together - it
OL,18,Fcan be a cookery class, a sports
OL,19,Fsession, friends meeting up and much
OL,20,Fmore.
